      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; FDA benchmark dataset is accepted as representative.",
      "rationale": "The FDA generic centrifugal pump benchmark dataset is a publicly available, peer-reviewed experimental dataset accepted by the regulatory community as representative for this device class. Formal test sample assessment is not required at MRL 2."
