      "rationale": "The validation and COU share the same pump geometry and operating envelope. Input parameter equivalency is qualitatively confirmed: fluid properties, rotational speed range, and flow rate range are identical between validation activities and the intended COU application. Formal equivalency scoring is not required at MRL 2."
